C<ExportPreferences> can be enabled for a StartExportTask
(https://docs.aws.amazon.com/application-discovery/latest/APIReference/API_StartExportTask.html)
action.

=head1 ATTRIBUTES


=head2 Ec2RecommendationsPreferences => L<Paws::Discovery::Ec2RecommendationsExportPreferences>

If enabled, exported data includes EC2 instance type matches for
